Revision history for Lingua-EN-Number-Format-MixWithWords

0.08    2016-06-14 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [dist] Replace Exporter::Lite with Exporter.

	- Remove unneeded POD section.


0.07     2013-09-11 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Fudge a couple of tests on rounding large
           numbers due to failure on many systems [CT].


0.06     2013-09-09 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Rebuild with MakeMaker instead of
           Module::Build because the latter is deprecated from core in 5.19.


0.05    2012-03-23 (SHARYANTO)

        - No functional changes. Remove dependency on old module Sub::Spec.


0.04    2011-10-25 (SHARYANTO)

        - No functional changes. Fix test [ct].


0.03    2011-09-21 (SHARYANTO)

        - No functional changes. Add alias package MixWithWords::EN.


0.02    2011-09-16 (SHARYANTO)

        [NEW FEATURES + INCOMPATIBLE CHANGES]

        - Add required 'scale' option to support short & long scale names
          [requested by Lars Dɪᴇᴄᴋᴏᴡ].

        - Internal: refactor common code to Lingua::Base::NFM.

        - Fix overflow problem with Number::Format.


0.01    2011-09-15 (SHARYANTO)

        - First release.
